Package utils

Class Benchmark

  • java.lang.Object
    • utils.Benchmark

  • public class Benchmark
extends java.lang.Object
    Benchmarks the given model. Calculates all the triples from the given model model that are contained inside the dumps that were specified.
    Author:
    Lukas Blübaum, Nick Düsterhus, Monika Werner
